# ==============================================================================
# Deep Learning Research - Datasets and Raw Data
# ==============================================================================
# Standard directories for holding large training/testing data
# (We allow data/ to be tracked so team members can share distilled text/JSON datasets)
# data/
dataset/
datasets/
raw_data/

# Common dataset/data file formats (to prevent committing massive binaries)
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz
*.tar.gz
*.rar
*.7z
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.npy
*.npz
*.parquet
# Note: csv, tsv, json, and jsonl files in the data/ directory are permitted for 
# sharing text-based distilled code-switched datasets. Avoid committing large (>50MB) datasets.

